  # CLAUDE.md Best Practices
  
  ## 10 Sections to Include in your CLAUDE.md
  
  [![Nick Babich](https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fill:64:64/1*DvFE_85Tc3fObRgRww9ZTQ.jpeg)](https://medium.com/@101?source=post_page---byline--1ef4f861ce7c---------------------------------------)
  
